Introduction

naevis (stylized as nævis) is a virtual singer under SM Entertainment. She made her debut on September 10, 2024, with the digital single "Done".

naevis is the first virtual artist under SM Entertainment. She is a supporting character in the aespa universe, helping and guiding the members and their avatars (aes) by opening the P.O.S (Port of Soul) to connect the Flat World, the Real World, and the Kwangya SM center.

naevis will use a voice created with artificial intelligence and content generated by AI. Her IP universe will expand through music, webtoons, games, brand collaborations, and merchandise.
